	<h2> Follow-Up Questions </h2>
	<p> Your goal is to make sure the interviewer has no reservations about you,
 demonstrate your interest in the employer, and find out if you feel the employer is the
right fit for you. </p>
	<ul>
		<li id = "list"> “Can you describe a typical day for someone in this position?” </li>
		<li id = "list"> “How would I be evaluated?” </li>
		<li id = "list"> "Do you have any hesitations about my qualifications?" </li>
		<li id = "list"> "Do you offer continuing education and professional training?"</li>
		<li id = "list">"What is the next step in the process?"</li>
		<li id = "list"> "If I were hired for this position, would I be going through any training prior to actually starting the work?"</li>
		<li id = "list"> "Is there anything else I can provide you with that would be helpful or questions I can answer?"</li>
	</ul>
	
